                     <interp inst="t18790630-600-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="arson"></interp>, Feloniously setting fire to a mattress and bedding in the dwelling-house of <persName id="t18790630-name-40" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18790630-name-40" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18790630-name-40" type="surname" value="EVANS"></interp>
